                        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; text-align:left;">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    In Gridcoin's Proof-of-Stake (POS) system, rewards are minted as yearly compound interest. Users earn their BOINC rewards when they stake a POS block.
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:10px;">
                                    In order to stake a block (and earn your BOINC rewards), a positive balance of GRC is required (This is the case for all POS cryptocurrencies).
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            There are 960 blocks per day that you can attempt to stake. An user with 1% of the total Gridcoin supply will stake approximately 10 blocks per day if 100% of coins are actively staking. Given that we don't experience 100% staking participation, your staking frequency estimation will likely be an underestimation.
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            The formula required to work out the quantity of coins to stake in a period of time is:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                    <code>
                                                    EstimatedDaysUntilStake=(1/(UserBalance/NetworkCoinSupply))/960
                                                    </code>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <code>
                                                    CoinsRequired=(1/(days*960))*NetworkCoinSupply
                                                    </code>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            The payout window is approximately 182.5 days. A staking frequency greater than this is potentially insufficient for solo-staking.
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            Thusly, the rate at which you are rewarded for your BOINC work is identical to the rate at which you mint POS blocks (since you're rewarded for DPOR on top of your interest payment).
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            Note: Your balance does not affect the magnitude calculation, only the rate of payment.
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:10px;">
                                    You need to register your CPID within the Gridcoin network, this is achieved by advertising a beacon transaction to the network. The beacon costs a small amount of GRC and it takes approx 24hrs to register your CPID in the GRC reward mechanism after advertisement.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
